meta.executedQueryString:
SELECT
  `date` AS "time",
  country AS metric,
  daily_vaccinations
FROM country_vaccinations
ORDER BY time

meta.executedQueryString:
SELECT
  `date` AS "time",
  vaccines AS metric,
  people_vaccinated
FROM country_vaccinations
WHERE
  `date` BETWEEN FROM_UNIXTIME(1491491363) AND FROM_UNIXTIME(1649257763)
ORDER BY date

panels.title: Vaccins : doses par fabricants

meta.executedQueryString:
SELECT
  sum(people_vaccinated), country
FROM country_vaccinations
GROUP BY country HAVING sum(people_vaccinated)
